TY  - JOUR
AU  - Greenwood, Robin
AU  - Shleifer, Andrei
T1  - Expectations of Returns and Expected Returns
PY  - 2014
Y1  - 2014/03/01
DO  - 10.1093/rfs/hht082
JO  - The Review of Financial Studies
JA  - Rev Financ Stud
VL  - 27
IS  - 3
SP  - 714
EP  - 746
SN  - 0893-9454
AB  - We analyze time series of investor expectations of future stock market returns from six data sources between 1963 and 2011. The six measures of expectations are highly positively correlated with each other, as well as with past stock returns and with the level of the stock market. However, investor expectations are strongly negatively correlated with model-based expected returns. The evidence is not consistent with rational expectations representative investor models of returns.
Y2  - 3/26/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1093/rfs/hht082
ER  - 



